It seems to show up ok. It uses grep and sed and with those it scans through all available sub directories and repacks any zips found with 7-zip.

It's a reeaaally ugly script which I'm quite ashamed of and probably should remake in perl to make it a cute one liner. It works fine on my windo$e-box though. As always, remember TIMTOWTDI!
